  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p700058/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p align=\"left\">\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201409/e33f8ccc37ff415594b77d846ac04e06.jpg\" /></p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n\tRumours about Apple&rsquo;s bending iPhone 6 Plus show no signs of dying down.iPhone 6 Plus能被掰弯的传言愈演愈烈。</p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">In a five-minute video, two 15-year-old boys step into an Apple store to try to bend a gold iPhone 6 Plus.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">在一个5分钟的视频里，2名15岁少年走进苹果商店想要掰弯一个金色iPhone 6 Plus。</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">They use so much pressure that the screen on the phone pops out, causing the teenagers to say they have to run away or &lsquo;they would have ended up paying for it&rsquo;.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">他们用了很大力气，以至于手机屏幕都崩开。两名少年说他们必须跑掉以免赔偿。</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">The boys then ask a shop worker whether or not an iPhone 6 Plus could&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/bend\" target=\"_blank\">bend</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">随后他们问店里的一名工作人员iPhone 6 Plus能不能被掰弯。</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">It is believed that the thinner model, as well as the use of aluminium metal in its design, causes the frame to deform.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">据信，iPhone6的机身会变形是因为做的更薄，加之使用了铝金属。</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">Apple has acknowledged there are issues with new iPhones bending under some&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/circumstance\" target=\"_blank\">circumstances</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">, but it added that it has only received nine official complaints.</span><span style=\"l